PARKING:
There are a variety of parking options near Atrium Two. Most on-street parking is limited to 60 minutes or less, so a parking lot or garage is probably the best choice. If you are unfamiliar with parkng downtown, you can find parking options on the Best Parking website:
https://www.bestparking.com/cincinnati-oh-parking/destinations/atrium-two-parking/?daily=1